k" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-V%E1%BA%A1n-L%C3%BD/Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-h%E1%BA%ADu-v%C3%A3n-t%C3%ACnh-t%E1%BB%A9-s%C6%A1n-giai-thanh-duy-%C4%90%C3%B4ng-S%C6%A1n-to%C3%A0n-b%E1%BA%A1ch/poem-EaKPWD2I71atervoOnhVGA">Tuyết hậu vãn tình, tứ sơn giai thanh, duy Đông Sơn toàn bạch - 雪後晚晴四山皆青惟東山全白</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-V%E1%BA%A1n-L%C3%BD/author-JSRpfYAHfq-c4bVKwnYGVg">Dương Vạn Lý</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/%E1%BB%A8c-mai/poem-MMsO2x9mBUyXun9cBP8M6Q">Ức mai - 憶梅</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-Ph%C3%BA/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-II/poem-OE49PRk9pb4zSGHDsXxK7A">Vô đề (II) - 無題 (II)</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-Ph%C3%BA/author-NMvfSgcxjBLOFSoPM09B4g">Liễu Phú</a>)<br></div>	</div>
